# Code of Conduct

## Our Pledge
We promise to create a welcoming and respectful environment for everyone.

## Standards
- Be respectful and kind.  
- Use appropriate language.  
- Help others learn and grow.  

Unacceptable behavior includes harassment, discrimination, or offensive comments.

## Enforcement
Issues can be reported to the project maintainers at [your-email@example.com].  
All reports will be reviewed and acted upon fairly.

